      <h2>Personal Pitch</h2>
      <p>
        I’m an enthusiastic and sporty person with a strong passion for football. In my free time, I love being on the field, where I combine teamwork, perseverance, and fun. I also enjoy gaming and watching football, and I’m always looking for new challenges to keep growing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function setLanguage(lang) {
      document.getElementById('content-nl').style.display = lang === 'nl' ? 'flex' : 'none';
      document.getElementById('content-en').style.display = lang === 'en' ? 'flex' : 'none';
    }

    // Default language
    setLanguage('nl');
  </script>

</body>
</html>